---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Cat Gogh Studio sells digital art, handcrafted art, and software artifacts for modern brands and creators."
    />
    <title>Cat Gogh Studio | Art + Software Artifacts</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
        <p class="eyebrow">Cat Gogh Studio</p>
        <h1>Professional creative products at the intersection of art and software.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          We help creators, teams, and businesses stand out with premium digital art, handcrafted art pieces,
          and production-ready software artifacts. Built with taste, delivered with reliability.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="#lead-form">Get pricing & availability</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="mailto:hello@catgogh.studio">Email the studio</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="services" aria-label="What we offer">
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Digital Art</h2>
          <p>Illustrations, character packs, assets, and branded visual systems ready for web, social, and product use.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Crafted Art Shop</h2>
          <p>Handcrafted pieces made in small batches for collectors, creative workspaces, and gift-ready orders.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h2>Software Artifacts</h2>
          <p>High-quality software components, internal tools, and polished product deliverables that teams can ship fast.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="proof" aria-label="Why clients choose us">
        <h2>Why Cat Gogh Studio</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cross-disciplinary expertise:</strong> one partner for visual quality and technical execution.</li>
          <li><strong>Business-friendly delivery:</strong> clear scope, timelines, and communication.</li>
          <li><strong>Scalable output:</strong> from one-off commissions to ongoing collaboration.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="lead" id="lead-form" aria-label="Lead capture form">
        <div>
          <h2>Tell us what you need</h2>
          <p>
            Share a few details and we’ll respond with the best next step, pricing direction, and availability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <form action="mailto:hello@catgogh.studio" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required />

          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required />

          <label for="interest">Primary interest</label>
          <select id="interest" name="interest" required>
            <option value="" disabled selected>Select one</option>
            <option>Digital art</option>
            <option>Crafted art shop</option>
            <option>Software artifacts</option>
            <option>Multiple services</option>
          </select>

          <label for="details">Project details</label>
          <textarea id="details" name="details" rows="4" placeholder="Goals, timeline, and budget range"></textarea>

          <button type="submit">Request a consultation</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
